title: Orson Scott Card | Complete Ender's Game series (Enderverse)
description:
Complete collection of Orson Scott Card's Ender's Game series, or Enderverse, including:

Earth Unaware
Earth Afire
Mazer in Prison
Pretty Boy
Cheater
First Meetings in the Enderverse [Includes: The Polish Boy, Teacher's Pest, Investment Counselor]
Ender's Game
A War of Gifts
Ender in Exile [Includes: Ender's Homecoming, A Young Man with Prospects, Ender in Flight, The Gold Bug]
Speaker for the Dead
Xenocide
Children of the Mind
Ender's Shadow
Shadow of the Hegemon
Shadow Puppets
Shadow of the Giant
Shadows in Flight

Still unreleased: Earth Awakens (2014), Shadows Alive (TBA)

Chronology: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:Ender%27s_Game_chronology
